snippet.title: Super Mario Journey to Infinity SSRM + F3 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for my upcoming SM64 rom hack, Super Mario Journey to Infinity. Made for both SSRM 2022, hosted by the SM64 rom hacking community, and F3 2022, hosted by Kaze. Both events are happening this weekend (7/29 - 7/31) so be sure to check them out as well!

Song used: The Phoenix by Fallout Boy (Nightcore version) 
You can check out this version here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7OIkJWB35Q
